s no  conditions of use  british american tobacco maxlargemediumsmallmobile british american tobacco  our brands british american tobacco  our brands quick navigation jump to content jump to navigation jump to search our brands worldfamous tobacco brands and innovative next generation products our brand portfolio is at the heart of our companys vision to ‘be the worlds best at satisfying consumer moments in tobacco and beyond’ we make the cigarettes chosen by around one in eight of the world’s one billion adult smokers our worldfamous tobacco brands drive our yearonyear share growth in our key global markets by meeting the needs of our consumers we are also investing in a portfolio of next generation product brands to meet consumer demand for potentially less risky alternatives to regular cigarettes including vapour and tobacco heating products these innovations demonstrate our commitment to meeting all of the differing preferences of our consumers with a choice of tobacco and nicotine products leading tobacco brands our business isn’t about getting more people to smoke or encouraging those that do smoke to smoke more it’s about really understanding and meeting the preferences of adult smokers with high quality innovative products so that we can continue to increase our global market share our five leading tobacco brands – our global drive brands gdbs – are dunhill kent lucky strike pall mall and rothmans they play a key role in our growth strategy and in  accounted for  of all the cigarettes we sold up from  in  dunhill dunhill’s roots date back to  when dunhill tobacco of london limited was established on gentlemen’s row in london more than a century later dunhill is our premium international brand kent kent symbolises progress through technology in the cigarette category and stands out as the most innovative and forwardlooking brand in the industry it’s a pioneering brand which has led the way since  lucky strike based on its rich legacy dating back to  when the brand was created by its founder ra patterson lucky strike stands for the true and original american cigarette pall mall pall mall is the third biggest cigarette brand in the world for more than  years its core proposition has been centred on offering adult smokers round the world a combination of value and high quality rothmans rothmans is an iconic brand established in london in  a timeless classic with highquality standards rothmans is finding increasing appeal among adult smokers worldwide thanks to a contemporary proposition other brands our portfolio of tobacco brands also includes other popular international brands with strong market positions in many countries they include vogue viceroy kool peter stuyvesant craven a benson  hedges john player gold leaf state express  and shuang xi other tobacco products as well as cigarettes our core tobacco product range also includes fine cut rollyourown and makeyourown tobacco swedishstyle snus and cigars next generation products alongside our traditional tobacco business we are also developing products that address consumer demand for potentially less risky alternatives to regular cigarettes we call them next generation products and our portfolio includes vapour products such as ecigarettes and tobacco heating products following the launch of our first vapour product brand – vype – in the uk in  we now have a range of products available across a number of international markets including france germany italy poland colombia guatemala kuwait bahrain and the philippines in december  we opened our first vypebranded store – in milan italy – at the same time as launching a new type of vapour product vype pebble our tobacco heating product brands are ifuse – launched in romania in  – and glo which we launched in japan in november  how they work cigarettes capabilities commitment ambition next generation products annual report  an exceptionally good performance read how we are delivering today and investing in tomorrow search s