in and distribution channels to training our marketing agencies in our vapour products marketing principles to ensure full compliance “being such a new category there is still a lot of debate and misunderstanding among both regulators and the general public so we’re particularly proud of our successes in building a constructive and transparent dialogue on regulation and product standards with the ministry of health and the national institute of health based on expertise and scientific evidence “it’s been no easy undertaking and we’ve still much more to do including further expansion across the country and introducing new devices and flavours in  “for me it’s been a very challenging yet incredibly fulfilling time and i’m excited to see where the future will take us” in the past five years we have invested over us billion in building our next generation products business and developing a range of products – including vapour and tobacco heating products we launched vype in the uk in  and by the end of  we had six different vype devices available to consumers while the range was in ten markets worldwide we also became the leading vapour products business in europe covering the uk france germany italy and poland search search   bats lse gbp   skip breadcrumbbreadcrumbhomemedianews and features  explore our world we are one of the world’s most international businesses and many of our group companies have their own websites   batpress bat press officebatpresswe are delighted with the overwhelming support we have received from shareholders says our ceo nicandro durante bitlyuifgep julreplyretweetfavoritereynolds americanrainewstoday rai shareholders approved proposals in connection with batmerger bitlyuzqvn julreplyretweetfavorite investors current uk share price p p   our reporting contact us      british american tobacco plc globe house  temple place london wcr pg  british american tobacco twitter youtube linkedin flickr skip general navigation set general navigation set 