ynolds american the wall street journal january   retrieved january     httpukreuterscomarticleukbulgariatobaccobatidukkbneq  tim whitmire associated press reynolds makes big move into smokeless tobacco salemnewscom retrieved  april    eagle star at euroarchive euroarchiveguideorg  september  retrieved  april    zurich to pay bat bn for finance units articleslatimescom  october  retrieved  april    nicandro durante chief executive retrieved  november    scorecard wills world cup cricketwebnet  february  retrieved  april    london symphony orchestra  thank you london symphony orchestra retrieved  august    constructors bar grandprixcom  march  retrieved  april    tobacco advertising ban takes effect on  july deljpneceuropaeu  july  retrieved  april    bat exits formula  tobacco sponsorship autoracingsportcom  october  retrieved  april    a b boseley sarah  april  how tobacco firms tried to undermine muslim countries smoking ban the guardian retrieved  february    nigeria govt hits tobacco companies with whopping law suit irinnewsorg retrieved  april    bannatyne takes on big tobacco bbc news  june  retrieved  april    kenyon rainier stebbins medical anthropology quarterly new series vol  no  jun  pp –  ian cobain and david leigh  october  tobacco firm has secret north korea plant guardian uk retrieved  april    press release cafca  march  roger awards british american tobacco nz ltd wins scoopconz retrieved  april    obscured by the smoke corporate europe observatory  june  retrieved  march    reuters c billion suit vs big tobacco starts in march   retrieved  september   ctv news judge awards  billion to quebec smokers retrieved on june st   cbc news tobacco companies ordered to pay b in damages retrieved on june st   jt international sa v commonwealth of australia british american tobacco australasia limited v the commonwealth  hca   october  austlii  doward jamie  november  bat fined for oversupplying tobacco in lowtax european jurisdictions retrieved  october  – v