pirit cigarettes and nicotine replacement productsbritishamerican tobacco was established in  and spread across the former british empire including india and east africareynolds traces its roots to  when richard joshua reynolds started a chewing tobacco company in the city that has been its headquarters since the takeover marks an end for what became rj reynolds tobacco which stamped its home state of north carolina as a center during a bygone era of smokings popularity through its winston and salem brandsthe companys links with british american tobacco date to  when rj reynolds tobacco co merged with bats brown  williamson unit creating reynolds american the two companies already have a technologysharing agreement in the development of electronic cigarettesbat projects saving at least  million a year from its latest acquisition through costcutting of corporate operations increased purchasing power and other supplychain efficiencies bat also expects to add about  billion of debt with the acquisition on top of nearly  billion at the end of last year the company said in a securities filing last monthshareholders of both companies approved bat buying the  percent of reynolds it does not already own the cashandstock deal is expected to become effective next weekthe  billion announced in january valued each reynolds share at  up from  offered in october the price is nearly  percent above the value of reynolds shares before the october offer bat said in a disclosure to us securities regulators contact john mcdermott at  or follow him on twitter at byjohnmcdermott tags reynolds american inc tobacco tobacco companies smoking pall mall tobacco industry north carolina raleigh ecigarettes british american tobacco mergers and acquisitions winstonsalem latest tweets a twitter list by postandcourier most popular articles collections articlesfbi investigating south carolina statehouse corruption could expand scope of state probechanges by myrtle beach to control violence on ocean 